    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b0391494-d119-4dad-8413-3d6f4020d7fe">
                Mr. M. Philips Price
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b0391494-d119-4dad-8413-3d6f4020d7fe" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/a6bc1f7b-d4a5-47d9-872a-e48fa2c16686/Ruhr(Six-PowerAgreement)#contribution-b0391494-d119-4dad-8413-3d6f4020d7fe">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs whether he will consider discussions with the six Powers who took part in the London Agreement on Western Germany with a view to defining more clearly the proposals for the international control of the Ruhr industries and the rôle of the German directors in those industries.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b0391494-d119-4dad-8413-3d6f4020d7fe" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/a6bc1f7b-d4a5-47d9-872a-e48fa2c16686/Ruhr(Six-PowerAgreement)#contribution-b0391494-d119-4dad-8413-3d6f4020d7fe">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-41f2e465-1068-40db-b847-e6bafa350e1f'>
            
<p class="">36.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-32d2b6ea-fdc2-4ce7-b26f-8a74c060028a">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-32d2b6ea-fdc2-4ce7-b26f-8a74c060028a">
