<p class="">Does my right hon. Friend agree that serious and important considerations are involved here, and that whereas a great number of us believe that international supervision is good, the international management for which the French have now asked is a horse of a different colour?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-70f027fd-8193-4047-b84d-a3b30478a18f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
